              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Promote 24-48 hours before the session on all channels — social posts, email list, stories, and push notifications. Establish a consistent weekly schedule so your audience builds a habit. Tease the specific topic or guest so viewers know what value they'll get. Acknowledge viewers who arrive early to create social incentive for punctuality.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
